track_notes:
I recommend getting as much elevation as possible on the hiking trails via Aussergweilalpe or Innergweilalpe. The bit going directly to Gweilspitze from Gweil is very steep.

The ridge hike from Gweilspitze to the summit is very pleasant and offers great views.
The south of the summit is very steep, but manageable. Its not possible to stay on the ridge on the descent to Gweiljoch.
